overview.en: Saipan Chain is a global payment network that uses blockchain technology to cross-regional and cross-device cross-financial service providers. It provides real-time, efficient, reliable and low-cost for financial institutions, businesses and individuals through payment clearing networks (and stable currency). Financial services are mainly used in real-life scenarios such as forecasting markets (gambling), entertainment venues, shopping centers, hotels, yachts, and aviation. It has been applied in Saipan, Jeju Island, Seychelles, Cambodia, Myanmar, Palau, Macau and other regions. Ant Financial + Visa is located in the blockchain industry.
